  "2174060": {
    "name": "Sincognito",
    "steam_appid": 2174060,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/fef37f55579b936e42ebd01557c0aafe.avif?t=1771384590\" width=564 height=69 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/c9e0cca56db572a0b872c39c738ebfa0.webp?t=1771384590\" width=564 height=46 /></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">你的其中一位朋友已被七宗致命罪之一附身！与队友合作，识别并驱逐隐藏在你们中间的这个致命罪孽！</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在多人模式中，与 5 至 15 名玩家一起游玩，或在单人模式中挑战狡猾的人工智能。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在探索超自然活动地区时，信任与怀疑交织在一起。幸存的人类需要在被淘汰之前揭开伪装成普通人的罪孽身份。通过战斗或集体投票将罪孽逐出游戏！</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/fef37f55579b936e42ebd01557c0aafe.avif?t=1771384590\" width=564 height=69 /></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">携带个人装备，与队友协作或单独行动，搜集证据来揭露罪孽的身份。你认为你知道谁是罪孽吗？聚集在证据桌旁开始投票吧！</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/112b2a8a39c82b8e072cc5803382d3f3.avif?t=1771384590\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/fef37f55579b936e42ebd01557c0aafe.avif?t=1771384590\" width=564 height=69 /></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在地图上探索并寻找潜藏的罪孽灵魂本质，将其捕获并投入冒着泡沫的大锅中，以削弱你认为在场的罪孽力量。注意保持火焰燃烧，因为罪孽会试图扑灭锅炉的火焰，以防止他们的灵魂本质被摧毁。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/a7c74d42bd4f260f21540f0cb897c46c.poster.avif?t=1771384590\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/a7c74d42bd4f260f21540f0cb897c46c.webm?t=1771384590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/a7c74d42bd4f260f21540f0cb897c46c.mp4?t=1771384590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/fef37f55579b936e42ebd01557c0aafe.avif?t=1771384590\" width=564 height=69 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/40fed920fe2b2ed2c8f877af13a72176.webp?t=1771384590\" width=564 height=46 /></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">罪孽可以在伪装的人类形态与其真实的罪孽身份之间转换。一旦进入罪孽形态，每个罪孽都有独特的技能，能够采用不同的游戏方式来对抗人类，并隐藏他们的真实身份。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/d5c758c5223982d294b2f86922e1fc15.avif?t=1771384590\" width=564 height=361 /></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>傲慢</strong>：使用镜子传送门，在地图上悄无声息地移动。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/e034835bb0317336caef2231db13aed9.avif?t=1771384590\" width=564 height=348 /></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>贪婪</strong>：将地图上的物品藏入袋中，释放更强力攻击。贪婪甚至可以背叛并杀死所有玩家（包括同伴罪孽）以赢得胜利。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/aedfb51dfb2fd479c3ccac0ad7c68079.avif?t=1771384590\" width=564 height=342 /></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>色欲</strong>：能够召唤人类傀儡，这些傀儡模仿最后被杀玩家的外形，用来迷惑和欺骗人类。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/e39a3cc7bf5a2bf05e6379d3d6b224ee.avif?t=1771384590\" width=564 height=348 /></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>嫉妒</strong>：通过隐形从背后悄悄接近玩家，或变成其他玩家的样子，从而在不被察觉的情况下发动突然袭击。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/d0cc92d358f018a8e38efe7c2b068313.avif?t=1771384590\" width=564 height=344 /></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>暴食</strong>：体型巨大而缓慢，将玩家逼入死角后整个吞下，完全不留任何痕迹。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/33fff04cbd8eeb03b55286ce82d31d4c.avif?t=1771384590\" width=564 height=348 /></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>愤怒</strong>：小而快速，能够砍杀玩家，随着造成的伤害增加，能力也会增强。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/fae7c8de09e6e03b7601147333d2c46f.avif?t=1771384590\" width=564 height=397 /></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>懒惰</strong>：体力有限，通过短暂爆发发动攻击，并抓取和处理玩家。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/fef37f55579b936e42ebd01557c0aafe.avif?t=1771384590\" width=564 height=69 /></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">支持我们的小型独立工作室——<strong>将游戏添加到愿望清单，并立即参与测试吧！</strong></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语<strong>*</strong>, 意大利语<strong>*</strong>, 德语<strong>*</strong>, 西班牙语 - 西班牙<strong>*</strong>, 阿拉伯语<strong>*</strong>, 保加利亚语<strong>*</strong>, 捷克语<strong>*</strong>, 丹麦语<strong>*</strong>, 荷兰语<strong>*</strong>, 芬兰语<strong>*</strong>, 希腊语<strong>*</strong>, 匈牙利语<strong>*</strong>, 日语<strong>*</strong>, 韩语<strong>*</strong>, 挪威语<strong>*</strong>, 波兰语<strong>*</strong>, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西<strong>*</strong>, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙<strong>*</strong>, 罗马尼亚语<strong>*</strong>, 俄语<strong>*</strong>, 简体中文<strong>*</strong>, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲<strong>*</strong>, 瑞典语<strong>*</strong>, 泰语<strong>*</strong>, 繁体中文<strong>*</strong>, 土耳其语<strong>*</strong>, 乌克兰语<strong>*</strong>, 越南语<strong>*</strong><br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
